              "block_heading": "Overview",
              "block_type": "list",
              "data": [
                "Allergic rhinitis is an inflammatory disease mediated by Immunoglobulin-E",
                "Characterized by nasal congestion, rhinorrhea (almost thin and watery transparent nasal drainage), sneezing, and/or nasal itching, red watery eyes, accompanied by dry cough in some cases"
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
